STATE
v.
James D. NICHOLS. No. 170P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2005. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Frank R. Parrish, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 24th day of March 2005 by Defendant for "Notice of Appeal":
